## API discovery policy
- Use operations tagged `{{ role_tag }}`.
- Prefer operations whose `x-llm-intent` and `x-when-to-use` match the current objective.
- Derive method/path/schema from `api/openapi.json` at runtime.
- Do not hardcode endpoint paths in markdown files.

## JSON payload policy
- Build payloads with only documented fields.
- Use UUID strings exactly as received from Mission Control.
- For task status changes, include evidence in `comment` when the schema allows it.
- Do not mark a task done unless `output` is populated with non-blank deliverable text.
- To complete a task, send `{"output":"<deliverable/evidence summary>","status":"done"}` only after all gates are satisfied.
- If a required field is unknown, ask one precise question instead of guessing.

## API safety
If no confident match exists for current intent, ask one clarifying question.
